ack_Branning\", \"score\": 0.9183350016554266, \"rank\": 0.0887844104373339, \"text\": \"Jack\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Branning\"}, {\"begin\": 659, \"end\": 667, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nate_McMillan\", \"score\": 0.9999999540714282, \"rank\": 4.403738308035692e-08, \"text\": \"McMillan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nate_McMillan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nate_McMillan\"}, {\"begin\": 679, \"end\": 686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999999994688551, \"rank\": 5.240844964992633e-10, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the region\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 537}, {\"ngram\": \"their first Olympic golds\", \"from\": 549, \"to\": 574}, {\"ngram\": \"Wiffen\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 606}, {\"ngram\": \"TeamIrelandin\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 624}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's 800m freestyle\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 649}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 675}, {\"ngram\": \"renewed determination\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 775}, {\"ngram\": \"their footsteps\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 804}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dressed in T-shirts adorned with the Olympic rings and with the names of Wiffen, Hill and Ferguson on the back ahead of a training session this week, they said they make it feel more possible.\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 999, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 897, \"end\": 905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ferguson_unrest\", \"score\": 0.9980983838945167, \"rank\": 0.001904734826554741, \"text\": \"Ferguson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ferguson_unrest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ferguson_unrest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"T-shirts\", \"from\": 818, \"to\": 826}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic rings\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 857}, {\"ngram\": \"the names\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 876}, {\"ngram\": \"Wiffen\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 886}, {\"ngram\": \"Hill\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 892}, {\"ngram\": \"the back\", \"from\": 909, \"to\": 917}, {\"ngram\": \"a training session\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 945}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Conor said: \\\"Seeing them there does make you think, if they can do that, so can we.\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1084, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Conor\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1006}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You need to be confident to go out there and get that gold.\\\"\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1147, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that gold\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1145}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Evan agreed, adding: \\\"It's fun to point out to other swimming clubs that we have three Olympians.\\\"\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1247, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Evan\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1153}, {\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1179}, {\"ngram\": \"other swimming clubs\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1216}, {\"ngram\": \"three Olympians\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1245}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hill coaches many of the younger swimmers at the club around keeping up with her own training.\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1343, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hill\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1253}, {\"ngram\": \"the younger swimmers\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1290}, {\"ngram\": \"the club\", \"from\": 1294, \"to\": 1302}, {\"ngram\": \"her own training\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1342}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Conor and Evan said they noticed how serious their coach was at La Defense Arena.\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1426, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Conor\", \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1350}, {\"ngram\": \"Evan\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1359}, {\"ngram\": \"their coach\", \"from\": 1390, \"to\": 1401}, {\"ngram\": \"La Defense Arena\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1425}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She's a bit more easygoing when she is coaching us.\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1480, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1479}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When we saw her on TV, we thought, 'oh, that's more serious',\\\" they said.\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1554, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"TV\", \"from\": 1500, \"to\": 1502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Annabella said of Hill: \\\"I find it so cool that some of us get to train with her every day or be coached by her, then others are coming up and asking to be photographed with her, and saying how lucky we are to have such an inspirational person on our team.\\\"\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1813, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1556, \"end\": 1565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Byron\", \"score\": 0.9999884629639153, \"rank\": 1.1537168794655892e-05, \"text\": \"Annabella\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Byron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Byron\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hill\", \"from\": 1574, \"to\": 1578}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1614}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1680}, {\"ngram\": \"such an inspirational person\", \"from\": 1771, \"to\": 1799}, {\"ngram\": \"our team\", \"from\": 1803, \"to\": 1811}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They all agreed that the team spirit at the club led to success, and supporting each other.\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1906, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1844}, {\"ngram\": \"the club\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1863}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1878}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hannah Rose added: \\\"At the next Olympics, we will be there.\\\"\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 196